Poor Maps 0.1
=============

 * Bugs
   - Crashes on startup
   - Crashes when panning or zooming
   - Preferences saved only on clean exit
 * Add UI to change tile source
 * Ask permission from OSM sysadmins
 * Add OSM Roads from OpenMapSurfer (need to ask permission)
 * Remove debug messages

Poor Maps 1.0
=============

 * Add geocoding
   - http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Nominatim
   - http://open.mapquestapi.com/nominatim/
 * Add routing
   - http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Routing/online_routers
